FIG. 1 is a schematic block diagram of a prior art coil surge testing circuit;


FIG. 2 is graph displaying voltage versus time for a response generated by applying a voltage pulse from a charged capacitor to a good coil of a coil assembly;


FIG. 3 is a schematic block diagram of the coil surge testing circuit of the present invention;


FIG. 4 illustrates a test fixture for the pickup devices illustrated schematically in FIG. 3; and


FIGS. 5A-5D are graphs displaying voltage versus time for a response generated by applying a voltage pulse from a charged capacitor to the coils of the coil assembly illustrated in FIG. 3.
